" * `A` &nbsp;&nbsp; _pirmais (vai vienīgais) pārbaudāmais elements_\n"
" * `B` &nbsp;&nbsp;\n"
"\n"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_rules_help_4severity_names.h:2
